Raw Cookie Dough
http://www.grouprecipes.com/66660/ok-to-eat-raw-cookie-dough.html#
edible raw cookie dough. NO EGGS!

5 oz.- butter or margarine
6 oz.- sugar
3 oz.- brown sugar
6 oz.- flour
1 tsp.- vanilla extract
Chocolate chips
OR
2 1/4 c.- butter or margarine
2 1/2 c.- sugar
3/4 c.- brown sugar
2 1/2 c.- flour
2 tsp.- vanilla extract
Chocolate chips

Mix up the sugars and butter in a bowl
Add the rest of the ingredients
Enjoy!
Stick it in the fridge with some plastic wrap if you have leftovers.